parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electrical Wiring Failure in Climate Control Panel
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the electrical wiring in the climate control panel can cause the blower motor fan switch to melt, leading to a loss of heat, air conditioning, and defrosting capabilities, which can result in poor visibility and accidents.
symptoms: The blower motor fan switch melts
the air conditioning and heating systems malfunction
and the defrosting function is lost.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The ignition switch fails to turn
the vehicle stalls or fails to start
and the airbag warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a malfunction in the airbag system, which can lead to accidents or injuries in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
and the airbag system may malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rusting and corrosion of the frame can cause the vehicle to become unsafe to drive, leading to potential accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The frame is rusted or corroded
the transmission or transfer case is hanging or has fallen out
the skid plate is rusted or broken
the control arm mounts are rusted or broken
the running board is ripped out of the frame
and the vehicle is vibrating or making grinding noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Lack of Drainage Holes in Frame Design
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of drainage holes in the frame design can cause water and corrosives to become trapped, leading to rust and corrosion of the frame.
symptoms: rust and corrosion of the frame
and damage to the skid plate

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cylinder head can cause coolant leakage into the combustion chamber, leading to engine overheating, loss of engine performance, and potentially catastrophic engine failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: coolant contamination in the oil system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling or delayed engine cranking can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
The failure of the camshaft sensor can cause engine stalling, loss of engine performance, and potentially catastrophic engine failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
Engine fires can cause vehicle damage, injuries, or fatalities.
The rusting and corrosion of the frame can cause structural failure, leading to loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Rusting and corrosion of the frame
particularly in the rear trailing arms and transmission mount locations

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission skid plate can cause the transmission to fall out of the vehicle, leading to loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Rusting and corrosion of the transmission skid plate
leading to its detachment from the frame.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear suspension can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Rusting and corrosion of the rear suspension components
leading to failure of the leaf spring bracket
and shaking or vibrating of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: and failure of the front brakes

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag can cause injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of an accident
and corrosion of the airbag components.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Frame Rust and Structural Integrity Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rusting of the frame can lead to structural failure, causing the vehicle to become unsafe to drive and potentially leading to accidents.
The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to become inoperable, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: Rattling or chattering sounds from the transmission

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Clutch Master Cylinder and Hydraulic System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch master cylinder and hydraulic system can cause the vehicle to become inoperable, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: Clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
clutch pedal sticks to the floor
rapid loss of clutch hydraulic fluid

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transfer case and 4-wheel drive system can cause the vehicle to become inoperable, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
The failure of the speedometer and brake system can cause the vehicle to become inoperable, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
